      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in impeccable, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the most exacting standards, it offers an aesthetic and mechanical profile that is indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer seeking unparalleled quality and a pristine automotive investment, this offering stands as the definitive choice.",
