    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and driven with so much love. You won't find a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is definitely the one! Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
