    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit benefits from a comprehensive top-end service, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and precise valve lash adjustment. The drivetrain consists of a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a refreshed limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with epoxy-injected plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, providing the telepathic feedback these chassis are renowned for. The exterior finish is flawless, with no discernible orange peel or rock chips, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. This is a turn-key, mechanically sorted masterpiece for the serious driver.",
